<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2024-01-26 00:49:17.621698</lastBuildDate><item><title>More guppies for the 7 people who upvoted last time.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vyti4Ug</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sSWSt9W.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vyti4Ug</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[fa273CartoonBreaker]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cosplay for YOU!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Yva5CR0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Hz0wjDB.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love crafting, makeup and cosplaying. I'm closing in on 400 cosplays and I love being as diverse as I can with characters. Noone is off limits. If I think I'll have fun, then I'll do it. With that, all I'll say is always cosplay for you! 

People will try to tell you that you're "too" big or small, too masculine or feminine, too old, not the right gender or skin color, not accurate enough, fault you for not making it, shame you for using certain materials, blah blah blah. 

Cosplay is your fan-art of the character and there's no wrong way to do it. Go for accuracy with someone else's take or give it your own twist. Cosplay one thing or cosplay all the things. Make it, buy it, thrift it. None of that should matter to anyone as noone is wearing it and living your life except you. Either way, be respectful, have fun and rock it! ❤️</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Yva5CR0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[knightmage15]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>My 11th Cake day. Here is one of my favorites</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/paQBT4X</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VKAxT3R.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/paQBT4X</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CheeseBalls]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Thank you grandma</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/BrwGB3L</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jhhMl2Q.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/BrwGB3L</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vladrichdemaclant]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Hellboy</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RqS07c9</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NQKfmH7.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ImVCBxh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QyoFT8D.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V6dvk3Q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2Uuy6od.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YsXyuCy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aCFYAWw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BptFZdm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RqS07c9</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[knightmage15]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Not Safe For YOUR Work, Maybe</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5V3rjjm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3X14Und.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But we're cool here.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KVDngW6.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1WsBzTa.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5pvHWYn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Z7p18d2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8Riv5Nv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I've had a couple of these days recently. Thank goodness my boss is awesome and she gets it.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/69A2abn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We're a remote team, the weather is a weirdly frequent topic in our group chat.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XzChP4Q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>One of us lives in New Orleans. I sent them this. Laughs were had by all.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cKQji2P.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This makes me think of a couple people we weren't all that sorry to see resign last year...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PZgDh0s.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Heheheheheheh.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J9Ijkz7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fucken Billy.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JHL2X8F.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Pulled this recently - "I've copied (BossLady) in case you have any further questions about our internal controls policies." He did not. It felt great.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0qAatFR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So many clowns, so few circuses. Or something.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mSDaPJu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Out of a team of four, three of us are extremely queer and one of us is our phenomenally supportive boss. It's grand.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ixthahi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A level of pettiness I truly aspire to.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VU7W9qx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Happy Tuesday! What fresh hell today, team?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8QeekM1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Snerk.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EYPNIdb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fortunately we don't work for one of THOSE, but this kinda makes me wish we did...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4uq9pa2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uJOIeWt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GJbTUFR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yeah, that's about how it's been so far.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yVL8gJW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VU3wscj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Eqqxy4A.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'm never one to pass up a good "could have been an email" joke</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/D0Hfzwm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This would be a great signature line.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZMdDlxC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>WHY IS NOBODY TALKING ABOUT THIS?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/v6YhMje.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>One of my coworkers has the most adorable baby I've ever seen. This is for her.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EWbZJDt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Have actually sent this to them already, I think...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0tAvlf9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/91PS7lC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8lw4RCX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yes, we work with him, we refer to him by his full name plus the trademark symbol.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iMOFjPX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Saving this for a problem client we're ditching soon.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/N9YwYeT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Text, email, same same.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/biqh0gP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Uh oh.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4BUX5wb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nwbmfek.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8lXggQb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Or when certain people start piping up in team meetings...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QcIIWle.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oops, gee whiz, oops.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9K6CSpj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aJKA4fU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KEIWbMK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/50g9FKr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yesss, contempt of gender.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Y6vLqoJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CjtQi6W.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SE73GUt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Genuinely might put this in my next OOO message.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9jgps5s.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This has big BossLady energy. Actually big Everyone On My Team energy.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/R1CnFBL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And she's like "Look, I know this is dumb, you can tell me to fuck off if you don't wanna do it" lolll</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LNiufY2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Janet Loaf tax</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yBgk3Rp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Happy Old Man Chaucer. Lookit them biscuits.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5V3rjjm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ShipofRockets]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Mating season is near.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/SdBMs5I</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5xriRf1.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WjlEPwz.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/SdBMs5I</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheReturnOfMadJuan]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>James Talarico</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8QgtuKY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3mBq1XN.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/emNhSkW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.jamestalarico.com/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8QgtuKY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[roaduardo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Gorgeous eyes</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/lFrCI7W</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o5m3HF8.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgu