;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>PROTECTITI</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NEo3tX3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CrazyViruss]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I'm old.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Ss1KUK0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/M4pG7tK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Ss1KUK0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vodray]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It wasn’t an accident</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Jz0BD4u</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JfbR3OM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Jz0BD4u</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BesticlesTesticles]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Beer Maid - Cosplay</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/74FadkL</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aMtizrv.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Had to share this because I realized how funny it was. My Oktoberfest Beer Maid cosplay from a couple years back (and this specific Gif I made for it) apparently blew up online without my knowledge in the background over the last couple years... Some folks pointed out to me last week that when you look up "Oktoberfest" on any gif reaction platform - I'm near the top, and now when you look up "beer maid" I usually hold the number one spot... I feel honored :P Especially since, little known fact about me - I actually speak German. So it's kinda cool that in the decades of Oktoberfest existing and Beer Maid crushing it, I would be up the go to GIF :P</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qonn5Ni.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Twitter proof... I'm not calling it the other thing...</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/74FadkL</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Alsoashley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Christian Right is neither</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wCzPeu6</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/C37iQvS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/Brcremer/status/1749671641573958047</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wCzPeu6</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DarkwingDuc]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>At Japan’s dementia cafes, forgotten orders are all part of the service</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NiZ9MNV</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8MtHNyV.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.instagram.com/p/Cz6W4E5uY4s/

https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2023/09/19/japan-aging-elderly-dementia-care/

This 12-seat cafe in Sengawa, a suburb in western Tokyo, hires elderly people with dementia to work as servers once a month. A former owner of the cafe has a parent with dementia, and the new owner agreed to let them rent out the space each month as a dementia cafe. The organizers now work with the local government to get connected to dementia patients in the area.

It’s a safe space where they can interact with new people, be productive and feel needed — key to slowing down the progression of dementia, a neurodegenerative condition that has no cure.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NiZ9MNV</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GlobalImageServiceCat]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>THURSDAY'S 100% TRUTH.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9CcFg1w</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PIqwOId.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#FuckClarenceThomas</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9CcFg1w</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[doxydad1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Well, now that you put it that way, no I actually don't want to fuck around</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/g5lCE7L</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pzJcKtS.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/g5lCE7L</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Hauntologist2]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I like your... dog?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AeLwoaY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9eNQ8fY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qMh8Gb4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vYajlGi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1achLvh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RCsjkgJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/dog_rates/status/1750250081201033639?t=0poCOkiHxbiLXZcCptcxjQ&s=19</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/AeLwoaY</guid><dc:creato